key_result_id.odf_period_type as odf_period_type, okr_actual_values.ACTUAL_VALUE as actual_value, okr_actual_values.LAST_SYNC_MSG as last_sync_msg, okr_actual_values.LAST_SYNC_STATUS as last_sync_status, okr_actual_values.SOURCE as source, CREATED.FULL_NAME as created_by, key_result_id.odf_period_start as odf_period_start, okr_actual_values.ACTUAL_DATE as actual_date, okr_actual_values.NAME as name, UPDATED.FULL_NAME as updated_by, OKR_ACTUAL_VALUES.CREATED_DATE as created_date, odf_ca_okr_actual_value.partition_code as partition_code, OKR_ACTUAL_VALUES.LAST_UPDATED_DATE as last_updated_date, key_result_id.odf_entity_code as odf_entity_code, key_result_id.objective_id as odf_grand_parent_id from okr_actual_values okr_actual_values JOIN okr_key_results okr_key_results ON okr_key_results.id=okr_actual_values.key_result_id JOIN srm_resources CREATED ON CREATED.user_id=okr_actual_values.created_by JOIN srm_resources UPDATED ON UPDATED.user_id=okr_actual_values.last_updated_by JOIN odf_ca_okr_actual_value odf_ca_okr_actual_value ON odf_ca_okr_actual_value.id=okr_actual_values.id JOIN (select 'x' pmd_analytical_partition_by, okr_key_results.id odf_pk, objective_id.odf_period_end as odf_period_end, objective_id.odf_period_type as odf_period_type, objective_id.odf_period_start as odf_period_start, okr_key_results.OBJECTIVE_ID as objective_id, objective_id.odf_entity_code as odf_entity_code from okr_key_results okr_key_results JOIN (select 'x' pmd_analytical_partition_by, okr_objectives.id odf_pk, odf_ca_okr_objective.odf_period_end as odf_period_end, odf_ca_okr_objective.odf_period_type as odf_period_type, odf_ca_okr_objective.odf_period_start as odf_period_start, odf_ca_okr_objective.odf_entity_code as odf_entity_code from okr_objectives okr_objectives JOIN odf_ca_okr_objective odf_ca_okr_objective ON odf_ca_okr_objective.id=okr_objectives.id where 1 = 1 ) objective_id ON objective_id.odf_pk=okr_key_results.OBJECTIVE_ID where 1 = 1 ) key_result_id ON key_result_id.odf_pk=okr_actual_values.KEY_RESULT_ID where 1 = 1
